1150
00:55:12.960 --> 00:55:14.419
[keypad beeping]

1151
00:55:14.503 --> 00:55:16.463
[man speaking indistinctly over P. A.]

1152
00:55:23.929 --> 00:55:26.765
[sighs]

1153
00:55:27.808 --> 00:55:29.643
[indistinct chatter]

1154
00:55:36.149 --> 00:55:38.569
[indistinct chatter]

1155
00:55:41.154 --> 00:55:43.323
- Uh...
- [tense chatter]

1156
00:55:45.242 --> 00:55:47.160
- Um...
- Watch it.

1157
00:55:47.244 --> 00:55:48.703
[chuckles softly]

1158
00:55:48.787 --> 00:55:51.414
[indistinct chatter]

1159
00:55:51.498 --> 00:55:53.500
Excuse me.

1160
00:55:53.584 --> 00:55:54.765
- Okay. so you're on the flight.
- [Whitney] Hello.

1161
00:55:54.849 --> 00:55:56.669
I wasn't able to get you seats together.

1162
00:55:56.753 --> 00:55:58.004
- but you are on.
- Hi. Excuse me. I-I'm sorry.

1163
00:55:58.088 --> 00:55:59.380
- We talked about this earlier.
- Oh. yes. sir. you are also

1164
00:55:59.464 --> 00:56:00.882
- on the list. I'm gonna check...
- Excuse me. I'm actually...

1165
00:56:00.966 --> 00:56:02.175
- Excuse... Excuse me! Sorry.
- One second. Give me a moment.

1166
00:56:02.259 --> 00:56:05.428
- Excuse me.
- Hi. Uh. four hours ago.

1167
00:56:05.512 --> 00:56:06.471
you stood right there and promised me

1168
00:56:06.555 --> 00:56:08.306
that I would have a seat on this flight.

1169
00:56:08.390 --> 00:56:09.747
and now I don't see my
name. so how are we gonna

1170
00:56:09.831 --> 00:56:11.351
- solve this problem?
- I am so sorry.

1171
00:56:11.435 --> 00:56:13.436
- What's your name?
- Audrey Nelson.

1172
00:56:13.520 --> 00:56:16.231
- Let me take a look. Ms. Nelson.
- Thank you.

1173
00:56:17.858 --> 00:56:19.234
[Audrey sighs]

1174
00:56:19.901 --> 00:56:22.820
Sorry.

1175
00:56:22.904 --> 00:56:25.615
Sorry. Sorry.

1176
00:56:25.699 --> 00:56:27.659
Sorry. [chuckles softly]

1177
00:56:27.743 --> 00:56:29.036
Sorry.

1178
00:56:30.261 --> 00:56:31.386
Sorry.

1179
00:56:31.471 --> 00:56:32.806
[Audrey] Why are you sorry?

1180
00:56:34.176 --> 00:56:36.762
[chuckles] Oh. sorry.

1181
00:56:41.048 --> 00:56:42.799
[quiet. atmospheric music]

1182
00:56:42.883 --> 00:56:45.010
<i>♪♪♪</i>

1183
00:56:47.929 --> 00:56:50.766
[sighs]

1184
00:57:18.919 --> 00:57:21.797
<i>♪♪♪</i>

1185
00:57:50.617 --> 00:57:51.743
<i>♪♪♪</i>

1186
00:57:55.680 --> 00:57:56.643
Hey.

1187
00:57:58.166 --> 00:57:59.709
You're Audrey Nelson. right?

1188
00:57:59.793 --> 00:58:01.628
Yeah. Hey.

1189
00:58:01.712 --> 00:58:03.147
We went to school together. right?

1190
00:58:03.828 --> 00:58:05.799
I'm Whitney... Solloway.

1191
00:58:07.601 --> 00:58:08.769
Noah's my dad.

1192
00:58:11.054 --> 00:58:12.833
[chuckles] Hey.

1193
00:58:12.917 --> 00:58:14.641
I have an aisle seat in 23.

1194
00:58:14.725 --> 00:58:17.916
Do you want to switch?
We'd love to catch up.

1195
00:58:18.000 --> 00:58:19.270
Sure.

1196
00:58:19.354 --> 00:58:20.717
You girls have fun.

1197
00:58:20.801 --> 00:58:22.274
[seat belt clicks]

1198
00:58:28.029 --> 00:58:30.683
[scoffs] So. should I
tell the air marshal

1199
00:58:30.767 --> 00:58:32.116
to be on standby or...?

1200
00:58:32.200 --> 00:58:33.810
[chuckles] No. You're hilarious.

1201
00:58:33.894 --> 00:58:36.544
Hey. I was just actually
catching up with you on Twitter.

1202
00:58:36.628 --> 00:58:38.797
Congrats on the new memoir. by the way.

1203
00:58:38.881 --> 00:58:40.625
And. um. I just wanted
to say hi to the woman

1204
00:58:40.709 --> 00:58:42.085
who's ruining my family's life.

1205
00:58:44.787 --> 00:58:46.964
Uh. wow. [stifled laugh]

1206
00:58:47.048 --> 00:58:50.639
